column1: unique expression to descript chamber and wellplate number
column2: unique alpha numeric(wellplatenumber and well location)

column4: "N/A" = animal removed or died already, no change day to day
"Molt, R-(molt dissolved)" = instar preserved, molting recorded. Not meg molt carapace preserved
"wc, meg" = water change, animal remains in the megalopea stage
"J1_frozen" = animal molted to J1 stage, both carapace and instar juvenile preserved via neg -80 refrigerator
"J1_EtOH" = animal molted to J1 stage, both carapace and instar juvenile preserved in Ethanol
"weekend" = refers to merged or individual cell to indicate no observations during the weekend
